txt.en: 'There are many ways to prepare food, and many different tools and ingredients used in doing so, but none are as important as the oven. If you want to make the finest of baked goods and cooked dishes, you need a superior oven with which to practice your craft. I think we should add one down near the farms.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
Farmhouse of the Sutcrofts: Superior Oven
